'''Arthur Donald Stuart Duncan''' (6 August 1875&ndash;10 March 1951) was a New Zealand golfer and businessman. He was born in [[Colombo]], [[Ceylon]].<ref name="DNZB Duncan">{{DNZB|title=Arthur Donald Stuart Duncan|first= Richard|last= Ives|id=3d19|accessdate=23 April 2017}}</ref>

He also played three [[first-class cricket]] matches for [[Wellington Firebirds|Wellington]].<ref>[https://cricketarchive.com/Archive/Players/21/21812/21812.html Arthur Duncan at CricketArchive]</ref>

